        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 9. Pagurus fungiformis, new species. A-D, holotype male sl 3.6 mm from Bitung, Sulawesi (sl 3.6 mm; MZB Cru 1506); E-H, female paratype from same locality (sl 2.1 mm; MZB Cru 1507). A, right second pereopod, lateral; B, dactylus of right second pereopod, mesial; C, left third pereopod, lateral; D, dactylus of left third pereopod, mesial; E, left fourth pereopod, lateral; F, dactylus and propodus of left fourth pereopod, medial; G, right fourth pereopod, lateral; H, dactylus and propodus of right fourth pereopod, mesial." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4618871/files/figure.png" .

